Package: ebaTools
Title: Evidence-Based Assessment Tools for Diagnostic Test Evaluation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Ryan",
      family = "McGill",
      email = "rmcgill@wm.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides functions for evidence-based assessment of
    diagnostic tests. Includes calculation of common diagnostic
    accuracy statistics, Bayesian updating of probabilities,
    interpretation of likelihood ratios, and visualization using
    a Fagan nomogram.
